{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/concatenating-strings-with-plus-operator","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Spajanje Stringova Plus Operatorom","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U JavaScript-u, kada se operator <code>+</code> koristi nad <code>String</code> vrednostima, to se zove <dfn>konkatenacija</dfn>. Mozete napraviti novi string spajanjem drugih stringova.</p>\n<p><strong>Mfano</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">'My name is Alan,' + ' I concatenate.'\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> Obratite paznju na razmake. Konkatenacija ne dodaje razmake izmedju stringova, pa ih morate dodati sami.</p>\n<p>Mfano:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const ourStr = \"I come first. \" + \"I come second.\";\n</code></pre>\n<p>String <code>I come first. I come second.</code> bice ispisan u konzoli.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244b7","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napravite <code>myStr</code> od stringova <code>This is the start.</code> i <code>This is the end.</code> koristeci operator <code>+</code>. Obavezno ubacite razmak izmedju ta dva stringa.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16802,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/concatenating-strings-with-plus-operator"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"const myStr = \"\"; // Change this line","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>myStr</code> treba da ima jedan razmak izmedju dva stringa.</p>","testString":"assert(/start\\. This/.test(myStr));"},{"text":"<p><code>myStr</code> treba da ima vrednost stringa <code>This is the start. This is the end.</code></p>","testString":"assert(myStr === 'This is the start. This is the end.');"},{"text":"<p>Treba da koristite operator <code>+</code> za pravljenje <code>myStr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/([\"']).*\\1\\s*\\+\\s*([\"']).*\\2/g));"},{"text":"<p><code>myStr</code> treba da bude napravljen koristeci kljucnu rec <code>const</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(/const\\s+myStr/.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"},{"text":"<p>Treba da dodelite tu vrednost promenljivoj <code>myStr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(/myStr\\s*=/.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"concatenating-strings-with-plus-operator","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/concatenating-strings-with-the-plus-equals-operator","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/escape-sequences-in-strings","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244b7","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fi